 pricing strategy from the council is to increase accessibility and excitement for community members. By introducing Alpha D1sks and Misprints, as well as Launch Party Goals, the council hopes to engage customers and keep them interested in their collection and album features. Using promotional disks is crucial for boosting engagement and maintaining the success of marketing efforts.",
